2026-05-15T06:33:03.6614887Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6615249Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6615435Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6615772Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6616304Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6616636Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6616951Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6617295Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6617612Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6617936Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6618210Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T06:33:03.6618369Z 32    -->
